parameters.description:
Use query building commands as conjunctions to combine or exclude keywords in a search:
word1 AND word2 returns results with both keywords included;
word1 OR word2 returns results with either (or both) keywords included;
NOT word1 excludes any results containing the keyword it precedes;
\"word1 word2\" combines two or more keywords into one exact phrase to search for it specifically.

